      "span_text": "Similar to, the LTE-U transmission ON/OFF condition is used to define a duty cycle which is shown in Figure 4 (e.g., 40% duty cycle: during the first two consecutive LTE-U frames, transmission is turned on and it is turned off during the following three frames)."
